name: Kissed in Her Kimono
description:
This project was inspired by this Kimono, which spoke to me with it's Care Bears color palette and vibrant floral design.  I created this headdress and strappy turquoise outfit to pair with it and fluttered my lashes till I could talk Olivia into modeling.  She is so stunning and absolutely captivating in front of the camera. Shot in Berlin, in the misty rain, before we ate tacos. 
*
Model is @olivialilith666
